snippet.title: Spar and Brawl
snippet.description:
Spar&Brawl. is a weekly news podcast co-hosted by Kam in the red corner and Sam in the blue corner. They discuss and debate some of the biggest — and least covered — news stories from around the world. As friends and sparring partners, they always promise to go light, but every now and then, a good old-fashioned brawl breaks out.

Contact us at sparandbrawl@gmail.com
